dct_title_s: Five Mile Beach : Wildwood Crest, Holly Beach, Wildwood and North Wildwood, formerly Anglesea, Cape May County, New Jersey
dct_description_sm: Includes key, key map and text. "N.J.C.M. vol. 4." Five Mile Beach is a stretch of coastline in Cape May County, N.J., now occupied by the boroughs of Wildwood, Wildwood Crest, West Wildwood, North Wildwood and a portion of Lower Township. cf. Website of City of North Wildwood, N.J. Historic Maps copy has sheet 30 (key map sheet for Five Mile Beach) of N.J. coast map series, vol. 4.
